insula-->\n[[Category:East Asian countries]]\n[[Category:Korean-speaking countries and territories]]\n[[Category:Member states of the United Nations]]\n[[Category:Northeast Asian countries]]\n[[Category:Republics]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1948]]\n[[Category:One-party states]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|the Democratic People's Republic of Korea|the Republic of Korea|South Korea|other uses|Korea|and|Korean Peninsula}}\n{{Redirect|NoKo|other uses|Noko (disambiguation)}}\n{{pp-semi-indef}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{short description|Country in East Asia}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Use American English|date=April 2019}}\n{{coord|40|N|127|E|display=title}}\n{{Infobox country\n| conventional_long_name                = {{nowrap|Democratic People's Republic of Korea}}\n| common_name                = North Korea\n| native_name                = {{unbulleted list|{{native name|ko|\uc870\uc120\ubbfc\uc8fc\uc8fc\uc758\uc778\ubbfc\uacf5\ud654\uad6d|italics=off}}|{{small|''Chos\u014fn Minjuju\u016di Inmin Konghwaguk''}}}}<!--Please do not add official regional/minority languages here; use the langbox template directly below, included specifically for that purpose-->\n| image_flag                = Flag of North Korea.svg\n| image_coat                = Coat of Arms of North Korea.svg\n| symbol_type                = Emblem\n| national_anthem                = \uc560\uad6d\uac00<br />\"[[Aegukka]]\"<br />{{small|(\"The Patriotic Song\")}}<br />[[File:National Anthem of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea.ogg|center]]\n| national_motto              = \uac15\uc131\ub300\uad6d {{small|(''[[de facto]]'')}}<br />\"[[Strong and Prosperous Nation|Gangseong Daeguk]]\"<br />{{small|(\"Strong and Prosperous Nation\")}}\n| image_map                = Democratic People's Republic of Korea (orthographic projection).svg\n| map_caption                = Land controlled by North Korea shown in dark green; claimed but not controlled land shown in light green\n| cap